# Lerngesellschaft / Learning Society

> A manifesto for relational learning, by Jonas Hertner. The thesis: one-to-one tutoring, done rightly, protects a child's curiosity, tests understanding through explanation, and gives what mass schooling cannot reliably provide — sustained relational attention. Published as a bilingual white paper at lerngesellschaft.ch (German, canonical) and learningsociety.ch (English).

